you can request a pickup of shipping pallets by submitting a request to recycling/moving services via an iservice request or call 924-1990 to request removal of the pallets. wooden pallets in good condition will be reused by fdo or by sjsu's shipping department. broken pallets will be placed in the wood recycling bin and will be either composted, used to make wood items like particleboard, or used to create energy at a bioenergy facility. located in: corporation yard office hours: monday - friday, 8 a.m. - 5 p.m. saturday and sunday, closed 